          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“Then the earth reeled and rocked; the foundations of the heavens trembled and quaked, because he was angry. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“Then the earth reeled and rocked; the foundations of the heavens trembled and quaked, because he was angry."
